{"tid":377182,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"［新MacBook］成日hi到行touch bar","createTime":"2017-08-27T14:12:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-01T12:33:13.000Z","uid":80736,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bbacd78ea52f4f5b82b761123356ca4a75ee9178","tid":377182,"uid":80736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T14:12:37.000Z","msg":"你地有冇呢個問題？<br />\n轉頭問題，你地點解決？<br />\n個pad太大，我用開mouse，好易hi到個pad"},{"pid":"e1e563f44610c7c2778bc619c15ff8b52e828608","tid":377182,"uid":80736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T17:44:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d38b502b32bc1b3616cecd1aee538876d9af541","tid":377182,"uid":80570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T17:52:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一撚樣 打打下字成日hi到個cursor彈去隻mouse到"},{"pid":"fa325d26307a31a9ec9a47ef28fd1b88b173fd5e","tid":377182,"uid":2192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T18:07:06.000Z","msg":"貼條膠紙上去"},{"pid":"a04affa8e59387715f213681313ae43e39e17352","tid":377182,"uid":20730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-27T18:23:48.000Z","msg":"Exactly same situation <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fa509f2e390ae2aed0a3495ae4021f21149df20","tid":377182,"uid":33579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T11:45:53.000Z","msg":"mac打手只會係windows post出現<br />\n同mr a一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫巴打推"},{"pid":"832052eed501e7a8f58408ea0e9a59184fa66027","tid":377182,"uid":80736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-28T21:04:21.000Z","msg":"原來大家都有呢個問題"},{"pid":"f6e85eb9b1f912530cfc14cdf6a58307e0fcdca3","tid":377182,"uid":42064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T01:51:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>原來大家都有呢個問題</blockquote><br />\n我淨係會成日唔小心開左siri，我跟default 放touchID隔嚟。<br />\n有touchID login快太多，都值得"},{"pid":"56b865b23794c6a5fd441fbcda4df2bf85f17c38","tid":377182,"uid":80736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T05:24:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>原來大家都有呢個問題</blockquote><br />\n我淨係會成日唔小心開左siri，我跟default 放touchID隔嚟。<br />\n有touchID login快太多，都值得</blockquote><br />\n我裝Window"},{"pid":"9be2ce6b9a89131fc162642e1cfc2cdb801c07fa","tid":377182,"uid":80736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-29T05:24:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>原來大家都有呢個問題</blockquote><br />\n我淨係會成日唔小心開左siri，我跟default 放touchID隔嚟。<br />\n有touchID login快太多，都值得</blockquote><br />\n我裝Window</blockquote><br />\n而且從來唔用密碼"},{"pid":"96dda03200244eec31ab504a37b9c38499a07a23","tid":377182,"uid":42064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T15:58:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>原來大家都有呢個問題</blockquote><br />\n我淨係會成日唔小心開左siri，我跟default 放touchID隔嚟。<br />\n有touchID login快太多，都值得</blockquote><br />\n我裝Window</blockquote><br />\n咁真係唔應該用touch bar model，喺Windows入面好垃圾，緊係要返f1-12先正，不過15吋冇計。<br />\n同堆個track pad喺macOS太正，一過Windows又係垃圾"},{"pid":"b2ab78d793d5be9f83c03d13a5aba5863762996c","tid":377182,"uid":80736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T17:29:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>原來大家都有呢個問題</blockquote><br />\n我淨係會成日唔小心開左siri，我跟default 放touchID隔嚟。<br />\n有touchID login快太多，都值得</blockquote><br />\n我裝Window</blockquote><br />\n咁真係唔應該用touch bar model，喺Windows入面好垃圾，緊係要返f1-12先正，不過15吋冇計。<br />\n同堆個track pad喺macOS太正，一過Windows又係垃圾</blockquote><br />\n你Windoe嗰邊係用F1嗰堆？"},{"pid":"df42c38ba0794ff903e59f710cd22e936370911b","tid":377182,"uid":42064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T06:00:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>原來大家都有呢個問題</blockquote><br />\n我淨係會成日唔小心開左siri，我跟default 放touchID隔嚟。<br />\n有touchID login快太多，都值得</blockquote><br />\n我裝Window</blockquote><br />\n咁真係唔應該用touch bar model，喺Windows入面好垃圾，緊係要返f1-12先正，不過15吋冇計。<br />\n同堆個track pad喺macOS太正，一過Windows又係垃圾</blockquote><br />\n你Windoe嗰邊係用F1嗰堆？</blockquote><br />\n好似有得喺boot camp setting開F1-12，不過真係好多餘，總之touch bar冇左兩個slider同touchid就好廢"},{"pid":"9b320fe9b6704f0722a6430e3e14e044ac244fa9","tid":377182,"uid":80736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T12:33:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>原來大家都有呢個問題</blockquote><br />\n我淨係會成日唔小心開左siri，我跟default 放touchID隔嚟。<br />\n有touchID login快太多，都值得</blockquote><br />\n我裝Window</blockquote><br />\n咁真係唔應該用touch bar model，喺Windows入面好垃圾，緊係要返f1-12先正，不過15吋冇計。<br />\n同堆個track pad喺macOS太正，一過Windows又係垃圾</blockquote><br />\n你Windoe嗰邊係用F1嗰堆？</blockquote><br />\n好似有得喺boot camp setting開F1-12，不過真係好多餘，總之touch bar冇左兩個slider同touchid就好廢</blockquote><br />\n認同"}]}